Rating: 4
I made this cake for my Mother's birthday, and it was a complete hit!! Everyone had two pieces. I used almonds and italian biscotti for the crust and it worked great. This is a cake that no one has ever tasted before. When my brother-in law tasted it he was amazed at how you could really taste all the different flavors. I might try this one with different types of ice cream next time.

